Package: a2a-db-backup
Version: 1.1.1
Architecture: all
Depends: sqlite3
Maintainer: A2A Team <team@greenhelix.net>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Description: Automated backup for A2A Commerce Platform databases
 Provides a systemd timer that runs hourly SQLite backups of all
 A2A databases with 30-day retention and integrity verification.
